License — TBD (To Be Determined)
================================

Hermes is in pre-alpha. The source is published in this repository so the
design and implementation can be inspected. Until a final license is chosen
and applied, the following applies:

1. You MAY read the source code.
2. You MAY clone the repository for personal evaluation and build the
   application locally for your own use.
3. You MAY NOT redistribute the source or any derivative work, in original
   or modified form, in source or binary form.
4. You MAY NOT use the name "Hermes" (when used to refer to this project)
   for any forked or derivative project.
5. Code contributed to this repository via pull request is assumed to be
   offered under whatever permissive license the project eventually adopts.

A definitive license — most likely Apache 2.0 or MIT — will replace this
file before the first tagged release. Until then, please contact the
maintainer if you need clarity on what you may or may not do.

